# Git Attributes pour StackPages CMS

# Auto detect text files and normalize line endings
* text=auto eol=lf

# Explicit text files
*.md text
*.html text
*.css text
*.js text
*.json text
*.toml text
*.yml text
*.yaml text

# Binary files
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.gif binary
*.ico binary
*.woff binary
*.woff2 binary
*.ttf binary
*.eot binary

# Shell scripts
*.sh text eol=lf
